From 72ac0ac8410bb84aeb7fbdaa08b25ea4ae9bf24f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Tue, 19 May 2026 18:37:36 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Polish onboarding and dashboard SaaS flow
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- dashboard-executive-summary: fix hardcoded 'Fresh' telemetry stat to
  derive from monitoringTruth.telemetry_freshness; add resolveRiskEmptyState
  helper with 4 setup-stage-aware empty states (no assets, no target,
  waiting for poll, waiting for telemetry); gate 'All clear' on actual
  reporting systems; show 'Monitoring active; no detections' not risk-free
- dashboard-onboarding-panel: remove 'Live API reachable' debug step;
  replace chip row with structured checklist showing step detail and
  current-step indicator (→); link to correct route per step
- runtime-summary-panel: replace debug 'What exists / Fix now' labels
  with customer-facing 'Setup status' eyebrow and next-step copy
- workspace-monitoring-mode-banner: add data-signal-type attributes
  separating heartbeat / poll / telemetry; remove internal debug copy;
  show recommended action only when status != live
- styles.css: add onboardingChecklist styles for new step list
- tests: add 26 source-level truthfulness tests covering empty states,
  telemetry freshness, banner signals, simulator labeling, and setup path

https://claude.ai/code/session_01QKgXwqyWfR67jtz3qrz55x
